snippet.title: SCP Fragmented Minds | 058 Official Teaser
snippet.description:
#scp #scpfragmenedminds #scpfoundation

SCP-058. A unique specimen with a deadly new characteristic never seen by The Foundation. Through the halls and vents, you will hear its haunting vocalizations, always letting you know it is hunting you. Encounter these creatures in Fragmented Minds
